OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudier
OL,6,Fthis evening with a few showers in the
OL,7,Fwest. Turning wet and windy during the
OL,8,Fearly hours with persistent rain by
OL,9,Fdawn. Generally feeling a little
OL,10,Fmilder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAn unsettled start with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, heaviest and most
OL,14,Fpersistent over the Welsh hills.
OL,15,FSomewhat drier into the afternoon
OL,16,Fthrough still drizzle in places.
OL,17,FWindy, particularly later around
OL,18,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
